Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:21.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寬恕促人前行 仇恨讓人停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:26.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:31.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒讓你一直停滯不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:46.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名為永不凋謝之花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:51.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也無法永不凋謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:56.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}認真活著就會有回報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:01.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此斷言的話語必定是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之幾十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:11.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之幾不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:21.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:26.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原諒你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くこの手で掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして？　いま　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が解らなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境無く燃える焔　 群衆が指をさす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと強くなって　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したいひとを想い　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}闇をこの手で払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這樣 追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要親手去緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 則無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強顏歡笑也一樣 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無法保護珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼？ 我會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無人知曉也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃盡萬物的烈焰 飽受非議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保護所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心懷所愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}親手驅散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}養父總是對哥哥特別對待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是對你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從小就嚴格地訓練你 為了讓你成為驅魔師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只是被培養成了保護哥哥的便利道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是自願選擇現在這條路的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟爸爸和哥哥無關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都瞄不準了 內心還是很誠實的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼自己要被迫為了哥哥做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至今為止你已經想過很多遍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而哥哥本人卻對你的辛苦毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已經受不了這種差別待遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害 好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你其實很討厭哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.97,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,517)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(1074,605)}雪中松柏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不會上你的當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才想保持冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一直以來就是這樣逃避自己的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:04.28,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼不能養啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很憧憬哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明明救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但在憧憬的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是要醬油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 那是哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼時候佈下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Corycia Melaina Cleodora Cleochareia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Bateia Drosera Solaia Periboea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}假裝打偏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}實際上是在用魔法彈畫召喚水精的魔法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真的很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少要對自己坦誠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我既喜歡又討厭哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我更討厭軟弱無能的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真正討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}水精之水牢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稍微碰一下就會攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然看起來是建築物 但果然還是魑魅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣下去就無處施加觸地印 並以此為中心張開結界了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且也根本沒時間去詠唱咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孢子囊附近有沒有能落腳的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我找找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孢子囊 好巨大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只聽了一次結界咒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說實話 我沒信心能完全記住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且就算張開了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要怎樣才能打倒那種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 那玩意好像巨大的肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒吃晚飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是的 居然還這麼淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說實話 我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那還不是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}座位猜拳 石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你猜拳輸了 這也沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是說這個 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是不能拔劍 你不就只是個拿著根棍子的怪力男嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就一點都不怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 下面有個岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有這裡沒有魑魅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 就在這裡一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你還沒有自暴自棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}話說你才是 別怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在大家應該都在做自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們也來做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂小公主就專心布結界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你說誰是小公主啊 信不信我戳死你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還不是因為你剛才一把鼻涕一把眼淚的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不想當你這粗暴的公主的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡 用不著你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們要贏 勝呂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們上 愛馬小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才不是馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道他不僅僅只是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 嘰尼嘰尼 巴薩拉 巴嘰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管是老爸還是他 都一直在一個人硬撐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}簡直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吽 怛羅吒 憾麥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂龍士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的結界咒 我確實聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火屬性的結界？ 到底是誰做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這煙花真美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂你好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是帥呆了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好帥啊 勝呂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姑且把結界布好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還是第一次召喚惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒想到會如此消耗體力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都沒有手騎士稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然能召喚這麼多水精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但技術還不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是你的答案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你比我想的更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就死在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把一個人類燒成灰需要多長時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我得看好時間才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像情況不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說不定馬上就要破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難怪這附近的小嘍囉速度變快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打倒了還會不斷出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龍士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}千萬不要鬆開觸地印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是鬆開了觸地印 結界就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道 用不著你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我死也不會鬆手的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別一驚一乍的了 小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都說了別叫我小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是現在就緊張成這樣 等下會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持好像成功張開結界了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們也要快點了 要趕在孢子囊破裂之前到達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要怎麼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}路都被孢子封死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造 這根錫杖給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩 快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}腐屬性的東西怕火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要用這個逼退牠們 慢慢前進的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先冷靜下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這麼點火只不過是個心理安慰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}單憑我們兩個 沖上去和自殺沒區別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持和大家肯定也會原諒我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不會有人責備我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家… 不只驅魔塾的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們的家人也在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真虧你能說出要自己逃跑這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不會逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是現在逃跑 我這一輩子都無顏面對明陀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}連你都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都把恩情 責任 血脈 明陀什麼的掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真是受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這種東西不值得賭上生命來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這種危急關頭 你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死了就全完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志 志摩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是那種偉大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不來的話 我就一個人逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}薄情小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓 少住持 父親 哥哥都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你最年長的矛哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是為了保護你和少住持而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的命是他救下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你今後可要好好活著 不能給他蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}關我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當我煩惱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就會問自己「如果是矛哥會怎麼做」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矛哥是志摩家的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矛哥到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是我的錫杖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我承認你是志摩家的男人 所以把它託付給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要代表志摩家 好好保護少住持和子貓丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這一切對我來說都太過沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼鬼明陀 血脈 恩情 全都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 修呢嘛呢嘛嘛呢 嘛呢修修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果真的能拋棄這些 那該多輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}錫杖著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此 八百造大人召喚了烏樞沙摩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我來詠唱真言強化你的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩你繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的假的 我一回來就讓我衝鋒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩對不起 我不該說你是薄情小人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孢子囊可能快要破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得快點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保 饌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真會使喚狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出來吧 保食兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出來吧 御饌津兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓牠們抬著師父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然很小 但很有力氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上次野營的時候 化燈籠也是讓牠們搬運的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 我不能集中精神了 安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}話說回來 我為什麼在做這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼那時候會想要幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己都搞不懂自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遇上他們以來 我的步調就亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總之 約定好的事還是要辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要活著回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同學 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什麼都願意做 你儘管開口就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特別是這傢伙 看著就來氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不用勉強自己加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為你很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乖乖讓人保護著不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保 饌 你們帶著師父離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才不想被這種半桶水使喚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在做什麼啊 我不能死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能拋下你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只會拖後腿 快逃啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小保 小饌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}師父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必須想辦法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求求你 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你現在不出來就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能一直這麼弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必須救神木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小 小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你願意幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要先救神木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無論孢子怎樣腐蝕 我們都要種上加倍的綠色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好厲害啊 小尼 太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然能讓綠男巨大化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你等著 神木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定會救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上吧 小尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧 奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修呢嘛呢嘛嘛呢 嘛呢修修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}視野變藍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的眼睛怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那一瞬間 我都本能地後退了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然我覺得你很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但可能還是小看了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那不是你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是執著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真虧你能知道我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼大手大腳地放火 誰都知道你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你個老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你糟蹋了我所珍視的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要讓你灰飛煙滅 給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:05.38,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第十集 不屈不撓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
